    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "A comozant wyrd appears to be 3 feet of buzzing, heatless blue or green plasma. Creatures near it find their hair standing on end and their bodies crawling with harmless but unnerving sparks. Those who have \u201cconversed\u201d with a comozant using illuminating flames say it uses pure emotion and image as concept and word\u2014a mixture of knowledge and ignorance."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>The only real feature of this flaring of electrical energy is a vaguely humanoid face that flickers and plays within its shifting mass.</i>",
